videos.headline: De'Aaron Fox gets the scoring going with a Lay-in off the steal

videos.description: Off the Louisville made jumper, Kentucky races down the other end in a hurry to find an open Edrice Adebayo for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Kentucky scores in a flash with Adebayo's dunk

videos.description: Quentin Snider finds Jaylen Johnson left all alone under the hoop and throws up the lob for the huge alley-oop finish to get the Louisville crowd fired up.
videos.headline: Alley-oop to Johnson sets off Louisville crowd

videos.description: Kentucky caps off a 9-0 run when Isaiah Briscoe makes the steal and then instantly throws the long pass to De'Aaron Fox for the jam on the other end.
videos.headline: Kentucky off and running turning a steal into a dunk

videos.description: Bam Adebayo pushes his way into the paint and creates a sliver of space to throw down a massive two-hand slam that leaves the rim rocking.
videos.headline: Adebayo muscles in for powerful two-hand slam

videos.description: Kentucky's Head Coach John Calipari discusses adjustments with Malik Monk's foul trouble in the 1st half
videos.headline: Kentucky's Head Coach John Calipari discusses adjustments with Malik Monk's foul trouble in the 1st half

videos.description: Kentucky's big men make a pair of blocks at the rim starting a run out by Malik Monk who gets the layup and the foul for the three-point play.
videos.headline: Two blocks turns into a three-point play for Kentucky

videos.description: 2H (15:56) LOU Quentin Snider made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Deng Adel.
videos.headline: Quentin Snider makes a clutch 3-Pointer

videos.description: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson discusses feelings after winning Heisman Trophy
videos.headline: Louisville QB Lamar Jackson discusses feelings after winning Heisman Trophy

videos.description: Bam Adebayo gets the ball inside the paint, and with three defenders around him, still throws down the monstrous one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Adebayo tries destroying the rim with one-handed dunk

videos.description: Bam Adebayo has been putting on a dunk show for Kentucky, this time getting the alley-oop from Malik Monk for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Adebayo keeps punishing the rim with alley-oop dunk
Quentin Snider lobs it up for the Deng Adel lay-in

videos.description: Off a missed shot, Louisville gets a rebound and, with quick passing, leaves Jaylen Johnson alone under the hoop for a slam that nearly breaks the rim.
videos.headline: Jaylen Johnson with the powerful one-handed dunk
Quentin Snider uses his cross over to punish the Kentuckky Defender
De'Aaron Fox makes the difficult shot to get the And-1

videos.description: 2H (0:11) UK Malik Monk made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Isaiah Briscoe.
videos.headline: Malik Monk's 1st 3-Pointer of the game is a clutch one

videos.description: Louisville Guard Quentin Snider discusses tough victory over rival Kentucky
videos.headline: Louisville Guard Quentin Snider discusses tough victory over rival Kentucky

videos.description: Louisville coach Rick Pitino joins Scott Van Pelt and discusses his team's victory over Kentucky, what he learned about his players throughout the game and preparing for the next three matches which include Virginia, Indiana and Notre Dame.
